  "remarks": "\n As a diamond mining company, part-owned by the Russian State, ALROSA is an entity obtaining a benefit from and supporting the Government of Russia by carrying out business in the Russian extractives sector, a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia, and carrying on business as a Government of Russia-affiliated entity.  \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
